"===== Initialize Plugin Manager === 
call plug#begin('~/.local/share/nvim/plugged')

" Add plugins here:
Plug 'preservim/nerdtree'

call plug#end()

" Show line numbers:
set number

" Display NERDTree on open:
autocmd VimEnter * NERDTree

" ALIASES Below
" Alias: add Clip command to copy text to system clipboard
command! Clip %y+
